name: Roy Tang
text: I hope he doesn't have Changnesia. Seriously though I wasn't even sure if HB was running until I read this article:  http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/389405/one-family-rule-driving-quezon-city-mayoral-bet-mad  Maybe I just automatically filter out any political ads I see on the street
